{"tid":789251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印尼兒童扮IS聖戰士拿AK-47紙槍 幼稚園引爆怒火","createTime":"2018-08-22T06:05:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T07:22:28.000Z","uid":75969,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cf5e2c554978c6a94c6ba1a37bf28bd0df5e3991","tid":789251,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:05:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpibMxs7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpibMxs7.jpg&h=4c7f9c9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">印尼一座幼稚園讓15位小朋友打扮成「IS聖戰士」上街遊行。（圖擷取自臉書Denny Siregar）</span><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕印尼一座幼稚園為搭上慶祝印尼國慶日（8月17日）的熱潮，竟異想天開讓15位小朋友打扮成「IS聖戰士」上街遊行，不僅每個孩童都穿上全黑套裝、手上還拿著AK-47的紙槍，荒唐的遊行畫面曝光後，幼稚園立刻慘被砲轟「是在鼓吹極端主義思想。」<br />\n<br />\n根據媒體報導，這座位在印尼龐越市的卡蒂卡（Kartika）幼稚園在印尼國慶期間，打算讓小朋友上街遊行慶祝，原本是歡天喜地的活動，校方卻異想天開，讓小朋友們打扮成「IS聖戰士」。這些孩童不僅套上傳統黑色全罩式的尼卡布（niqab）罩袍，只能露出眼部，同時手上還拿著用紙板所做成的「AK-47步槍」，一共15名上街遊行。有目擊者將此遊行畫面拍下上傳後，頓時爆發爭議，不少網友痛批「幼稚園是在鼓吹極端主義。」<br />\n<br />\n面對外界批評，<span style=\"color: red;\">幼稚園園長在20日出面澄清，他們想傳達的是「伊斯蘭的奮鬥與困難」，並不是外界所想的，「灌輸學童暴力思想」和「提倡極端主義。」他還坦言，會選這樣的衣服，是想替家長省錢，才從儲藏室拿出去年的舊衣改造</span>，引起這麼大的風波，深感歉意。<br />\n<br />\n儘管如此園方已經公開道歉解釋，然而網友仍感到相當不滿，質疑「為何要讓小孩子拿紙做的步槍？」而印尼國會議長班邦（Bambang Soesatyo）也對幼稚園的遊行裝扮大力抨擊，表示這是「令人非常擔心的事」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0pPIB5N1moE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0pPIB5N1moE&d=E20NNy%2BV54F%2FbQl62HlGIP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=3e503785\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0pPIB5N1moE</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2526615\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2526615&d=E20NNy%2BV54F%2FbQl62HlGIP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=de1f86bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2526615&h=3d0b7ff6\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2526615</a>"},{"pid":"c8f38c38508b7269cc33ed3cc14ce9ec73838b15","tid":789251,"uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:06:58.000Z","msg":"諗起isis訓練細路殺人條片 槍槍爆頭"},{"pid":"a617f387643e546e89048c17660048197f2b26e1","tid":789251,"uid":132587,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:07:33.000Z","msg":"印尼同印度係支那之後最應該滅既國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191825da6e49d389bfc0ec1a6fb1364926d25469","tid":789251,"uid":17103,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:10:34.000Z","msg":"<strong>會選這樣的衣服，是想替家長省錢，才從儲藏室拿出去年的舊衣改造 </strong><br />\n<br />\n真係戇鳩先信"},{"pid":"e259f5b748503ee7efa4f4b04ff21f92dda6e0f7","tid":789251,"uid":55597,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a617f387643e546e89048c17660048197f2b26e1","tid":789251,"uid":132587,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:07:33.000Z","msg":"印尼同印度係支那之後最應該滅既國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:11:59.000Z","msg":"印度"},{"pid":"88f68784e33dbc8f73b32acd5b481afc2efa89dc","tid":789251,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:40:06.000Z","msg":"印尼賤種"},{"pid":"eb122e512fbccd571fc734c581e9f26a63a8b9c0","tid":789251,"uid":46933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:45:43.000Z","msg":"isis = 伊斯蘭的奮鬥"},{"pid":"1b92796f5552bff141919d139dc9211bb3c87133","tid":789251,"uid":50595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a617f387643e546e89048c17660048197f2b26e1","tid":789251,"uid":132587,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:07:33.000Z","msg":"印尼同印度係支那之後最應該滅既國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:52:47.000Z","msg":"三個國家加埋都差唔多世界一半人口 <img sr